<center><h1>Welcome to the Advanced Calculator</h1></center>
<br />
<p>This is the advanced calculator. It will calculate the power of a number or the square root of a number.</p>
<p>To begin enter the first number into the first box.</p>
<p>Then put what you want to do, into the second. Power or root.</p>
<p>If you are calculating the root, ignore the final box and hit calculate. Else to work out the power, enter your second number and go!</p>
<br />
<center>
<h4>Simple! Right?</h4>
<br />

<form method="get" action="/calculate">
  <input type="number" name="first_number" placeholder="first number" step="0.01" value="<% @first_number %>">
  <input type="text" name="operator" placeholder="power / root">
  <input type="number" name="second_number" placeholder="second number" step="0.01" value="<% @second_number %>">
  <button>CALCULATE!</button>
</form>
</center>